"ngram\": \"the city's mayor\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"the risks\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"pollution\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2002}, {\"ngram\": \"regular tests\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"the water quality\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"unhealthy levels\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"contaminants\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"rainy days\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meares said she had faith in the assurances of the organisers on the matter of water safety but would not be dictating any action to athletes if tests showed the water was not safe.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Meares\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"the assurances\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisers\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"water safety\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"any action\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"tests\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a point of us stepping in to say 'we will not let you swim'.\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2314}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately it's the choice of the athlete,\\\" Meares explained.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the choice\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"Meares\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are not going to put any athlete in an environment that risks their wellbeing, that information will be given to them and that choice will ultimately be theirs.\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any athlete\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"an environment\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"their wellbeing\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"that information\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2530}, {\"ngram\": \"that choice\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Try standing in front of an Olympian who's trained for their whole life when they have the chance to swim and ... tell them 'no'.\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2626, \"end\": 2634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999996094200777, \"rank\": 3.9057140370893936e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2619}, {\"ngram\": \"their whole life\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not going to happen.\\\"\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team medical director Dr Carolyn Broderick said the AOC had experience of protecting athletes from potential infection after similar concerns about theopen water swimming venues at the 2016 Rio Games.\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2781, \"end\": 2788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Culliton\", \"score\": 0.9869505588402596, \"rank\": 0.010542936424873008, \"text\": \"Carolyn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Culliton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Culliton\"}, {\"begi